description: Submission of reserved matters pursuant to outline planning permission dated 14th November 2013 (ref: 2011/02001/OUT); relating to layout; scale; appearance and landscaping; submitted for approval for the following Development Parcels in LBHF: BW05-1; BW05-2; BW07-2; BW07-3; LP-4 (part); LP-6 and LP-9 (part); comprising a mix use development of 690 residential units and 4,895 sqm (GEA) of commercial floor space (Use Class A1-A5), provision of landscaped public and private open space; and associated cycle and car parking spaces at basement and ground level.
secondary_street_name: West Kensington And Gibbs Green Housing Estates
